      "content": "i hear you, but resting doesn't change the fact that the stuff is still there waiting for me. i'm just tired of fighting it. when i say i want it all to be over, i don't mean like a nap or a break. i mean i just want the struggle to stop for good. it feels like the only way to actually find peace is to just give up on everything.",
